column5: In light of St. Paddy's Day.  Dan Jenkins's list of Mankind's 10 Stages of Drunkenness:   Witty and Charming  Rich and Powerful  Benevolent  Clairvoyant  "Forget" Dinner (or something similar)  Patriotic  Crank Up the Enola Gay  Witty and Charming, Part II  Invisible  Bulletproof   Please celebrate safely.
Or any statement that starts  with........."Hey guys...Watch This!!!!"
